    <div class="col-sm-9" id="shortBio">
		<h4><strong>Resource Allocation in Cognitive Radio Networks (CRNs) [inactive]</strong></h4>
		<p>In this project, we investigate the resource allocation problem in Cognitive Radio Networks (CRNs) using evolutionary algorithms, such as Genetic Algorithm (GA), Harmony Search (HS), and Particle Swarm Optimization (PSO) algorithms.</p>
